{
  "title": "Floral Velvety Australian Fruit Toast",
  "description": "A post-workout Australian dish featuring a mix of exotic fruits, topped with a velvety mascarpone cream and a hint of rose petals, served on toasted sourdough bread.",
  "cuisine": "australian",
