  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 200°C (400°F).",
    "Slice the sourdough bread into 1-inch thick slices and toast until lightly browned.",
    "In a medium-sized bowl, mix together the mascarpone cheese, honey, and rose petal jam until well combined.",
    "Arrange the toasted bread slices on a serving plate or individual plates.",
    "Top each bread slice with a dollop of the mascarpone mixture.",
    "Arrange the sliced strawberries, kiwi, blueberries, and raspberries on top of the mascarpone cream.",
    "Drizzle the lemon juice over the fruit.",
    "Dust the confectioners' sugar over the top of the fruit.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
